title: iPad & iPhone User Issue 83 - 2014  UK
description:
iPad & iPhone User Issue 83 - 2014  UK

116 Pages | True PDF | English | 3 MB 


iPad & iPhone User is the only magazine you need to the world of the iPad, iPhone and iPod Touch. Get more out of your Apple device with our step-by-step tutorials, straight forward buying advice and expert reviews of the latest apps, games and accessories.. Each issue is packed with step-by-step tutorials and features on how to get the most from your apps and services like iCloud, iTunes Match, iPhoto, GarageBand, iMovie, Pages and Keynote, as well as all the latest apps. Anyone from a complete iPad and iPhone beginner to hardcore power users will learn more about their beloved Apple device.
